#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Gilānavagga"
msgstr "2. Sick"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Ariyasutta"
msgstr "19. Noble"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.19:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ariyā niyyānikā nīyanti "
"takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when these seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated "
"they are noble and emancipating, and bring one who practices them to the "
"complete ending of suffering."

msgctxt "sn46.19:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.19:1.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.19:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā ariyā niyyānikā "
"nīyanti takkarassa sammā dukkhakkhayāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"When these seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they are "
"noble and emancipating, and bring one who practices them to the complete "
"ending of suffering.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.19:1.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
